title: Dasaprakash
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Pizza, International, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out, South Indian
description: Serves authentic South Indian vegetarian cuisine, along with signature vegetarian continental dishes like lasagne, spice corn toast, spaghetti burmese, mexican pizza, just to name a few. Offers juices and american ice cream sundaes. Provides themed atmosphere. Entrees are inspired by recipes handed down from generations using the freshest ingredients and spices.
